ploys.description:
Whenever a friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR opératif is fighting, or has a Conceal order and is retaliating,
add 1 to the Atk stat of its melee weapons (to a maximum of 4) and they have the Balanced weapon rule;
if the weapon already has that weapon rule, it has the Ceaseless weapon rule instead of Balanced.

Use this firefight ploy when it's your turn to activate a opératif allié. Select one friendly HUNTER CLADE LEADER opératif and one other ready friendly HUNTER CLADE opératif visible to and within 3" of that LEADER opératif;
activate one of them as normal. When that first opératif allié you activate is expended, you can activate the other opératif allié before your opponent activates.
When that other opératif is expended, your opponent then activates as normal. Whenever you use this ploy, you cannot select more than one HUNTER CLADE SICARIAN opératif.

Use this Firefight Ploy when an opératif ennemi is shooting or fighting a friendly RATLING opératif (excluding OGRYN or BULLGRYN) and you are allocating a die to block.
If it is a succès normal, it can block one unresolved succès critique;
if it is a succès critique, it can block two unresolved successes (normal or critical).
